chamber, she gave way to a passion of tears. She 
could have torn the very counterpane to tatters. 



 

To be sent away the whole week through ! Oh, 
what could she do to circumvent this old woman ? 

She lay there on her bed half the night, it 
seemed to her. But it could not have been, 
