ten thinks she must have inhaled the flames. 
Oh, when will the doctor come ! " 

Dead ! Bessie had not thought of such an 
ending. She stood horrified. 

" Oh, she will get well again. She is so 
strong " 

" How could it have happened ? " 

" I think she heard us talking and came 
in here. She must have done something. The 
